{"tid":369320,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE CHEM Drying property 問題","createTime":"2017-08-22T08:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T16:20:19.000Z","uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50b9f028772d841d3f42a96e9965a50f15a49bbc","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"點解Anhydrous calcium chloride 可以 dry moist SO2 但Calcium oxide唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCalcium oxide 唔係都會absorb moisture?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a1ae034867b60222814513eb222525c270128f","tid":369320,"uid":61423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解Anhydrous calcium chloride 可以 dry moist SO2 但Calcium oxide唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCalcium oxide 唔係都會absorb moisture?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCaO = metal oxide = base<br />\nSO2 is acidic which will react with CaO (neutralization)"},{"pid":"547d4f76359e639b0b69bc26105d7163b852023b","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"咁conc. H2SO4 可唔可以Dry HCl (g)???<br />\n2010條CE話唔得 但2011又話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4311a89f318e3efc21772d63a982b3020b62fbdf","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8ca1e8d77bf479c61d21ba92461b72e28a786781","tid":369320,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42bf1d168535c7897c322fbb89848b978b570736","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:16:05.000Z","msg":"Sor電話影Mon好白痴但快D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl