ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哦 好簡單<br />\n<br />\n不過你先答我第一幅圖A你睇法"},{"pid":"c89135a5cda3787fb0b65edb321da1fff6c25bd8","tid":369320,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d256df308a4fcd55ca20a7bdaad48667ea75ad71","tid":369320,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sor電話影Mon好白痴但快D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021445_6f36ba5c59a3e82feeff7014993bec69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021445_6f36ba5c59a3e82feeff7014993bec69.jpg&h=21d1c4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條答案係D 即係A唔啱<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021503_e5c784fe7293c14bb11bfe779a5eed4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021503_e5c784fe7293c14bb11bfe779a5eed4e.jpg&h=fa1154ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但呢題個答案係D 即係HCl都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求高手賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哦 好簡單<br />\n<br />\n不過你先答我第一幅圖A你睇法</blockquote><br />\n我一步一步教你推個答案<br />\n而唔係死背<br />\n<br />\n第一幅圖比埋set up問你set up下得唔得<br />\n第二幅圖純粹問得唔得"},{"pid":"e2e19fd88bcb497c5654e952c4a440c9f6e52e0a","tid":369320,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sor電話影Mon好白痴但快D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/021445_6f36ba5c59a3e82feeff7014993bec69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F021445_6f36ba5c59a3e82feeff7014993bec69.jpg&h=21d1c4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><