mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79918029d152655f1f811734e4ced52bb0144cb0","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491abc99f2583eee59e45922b28171850751d691","tid":369320,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左"},{"pid":"524ce3dbdbb1f9b445f0a1028b27dc61d76f552f","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n咁屌錯位H2SO4都應該Dry 到HCl 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe9110bf73a251ac76b69e14f146f8b2dd0983e","tid":369320,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n咁屌錯位H2SO4都應該Dry 到HCl 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我叫你解釋你諗法。<br />\n我再一步一步話你知你logical flow有咩錯<br />\n<br />\n你唔盡量諗而直接求答案，你唔會學好"},{"pid":"d6f2478b3feee0dc584cc6565bdb9918f71c2b37","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n咁屌錯位H2SO4都應該Dry 到HCl 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我叫你解釋你諗法。<br />\n我再一步一步話你知你logical flow有咩錯<br />\n<br />\n你唔盡量諗而直接求答案，你唔會學好</blockquote><br />\n我嘅睇法:<br />\nHCl can still be dried by H2SO4, but it can't leave the bottle since the pressure causes H2SO4 to be sucked up. Therefore, HCl can be dried but cannot be obtained."},{"pid":"8432db3c157f0a77d9426e7de7f59cbb05eabe09","tid":369320,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n咁屌錯位H2SO4都應該Dry 到HCl 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我叫你解釋你諗法。<br />\n我再一步一步話你知你logical flow有咩錯<br />\n<br />\n你唔盡量諗而直接求答案，你唔會學好</blockquote><br />\n我嘅睇法:<br />\nHCl can still be dried by H2SO4, but it can't leave the bottle since the pressure causes H2SO4 to be sucked up. Therefore, HCl can be dried but cannot be obtained.</blockquote><br />\nOr the HCl can't dissolve in H2SO4. That's why it cannot be dried? <br />\nBut this seems wrong since H2SO4 can absorb moisture even from the air."},{"pid":"7d9c7f2910a25150b71cc3f0d00227018f6361a0","tid":369320,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果屌錯位air pressure會令到佢吸H2SO4上去而唔係HCl right?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n咁屌錯位H2SO4都應該Dry 到HCl 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我叫你解釋你諗法。<br />\n我再一步一步話你知你logical flow有咩錯<br />\n<br />\n你唔盡量諗而直接求答案，你唔會學好</blockquote><br />\n我嘅睇法:<br />\nHCl can still be dried by H2SO4, but it can't leave the bottle since the pressure causes H2SO4 to be sucked up. Therefore, HCl can be dried but cannot be obtained.</blockquote><br />\nOr the HCl can't dissolve in H2SO4. That's why it cannot be dried? <br />\nBut this seems wrong since H2SO4 can absorb moisture even from the air.</blockquote><br />\n最主要個點你答到, 但collect唔到唔關suck up事。你答suck up邏輯上唔正確。<br />\n<br />\n佢collect唔到dry HCl(g) since collecting tube is displaced in a wrong position.<br />\n<br />\nGiven the collecting tube is wrong displaced,<br />\n<br />\nSince the con. H2SO4 contains very little amount of water, the dry HCl can't be dissolved in and thus be collected through collecting tube."},{"pid":"4be6e466d656d8d42f904fecb9bccd769fb69aa6","tid":369320,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"如果佢問你A有咩hazard，你答con h2so4 will be collected instead due to pressure gradient 咁就岩<br />\n<br />\n但collect唔到dry hcl(g)就唔關con h2so4 is collected instead 事"},{"pid":"86fb4945f179d2d3f68595103c3e47dc024525ec","tid":369320,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解Anhydrous calcium chloride 可以 dry moist SO2 但Calcium oxide唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCalcium oxide 唔係都會absorb moisture?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCaO = metal oxide = base<br />\nSO2 is acidic which will react with CaO (neutralization)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046db0413668f9bc174d9bd2a0585da937e41e37","tid":369320,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T19:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢問你A有咩hazard，你答con h2so4 will be collected instead due to pressure gradient 